        <updateDate>2010-03-25T15:13:59Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Broadband Opportunity and Affordability Act - Amends the Communications Act of 1934 to require the Federal Communications Commission (FCC) to implement a two-year pilot program to expand the Lifeline program to reduce the cost of broadband service for low-income consumers. </p>]]></text>
      </summary>
